# Configuraiton for SIN
host !security-bastions-prod* *.sin*.amazon.com *.sin*.amazon.com. *.sin? *.sin?? *.ap-southeast-1.amazon.com *.ap-southeast-1.amazon.com. *.ap-southeast-1
